Okay, here's the deal. I'm currently at coordinate (41, 8), having just moved northwest from (42, 9). I'm seeing a dark area around me – the map is the key here. It's showing these dots, which I'm interpreting as floor tiles. My current location, represented by '@', is on row 8 (looks like it's zero-indexed from the top, which makes sense). The surrounding map paints the picture of a small room or corridor.

